extendedInfo.description: Gems Rising is an action-puzzle game where gems rise up the screen at a rapid rate and are cleared by creating matches of three or more gems. You create matches by moving the gems left and right, and don't let the Gems get to the top! Featuring multiple game modes, high scores, and an enchanting soundtrack, Gems Rising is sure to entertain.

reviews.title: Fun puzzle game for a quick break
reviews.comment: Gems Rising is a fun game to play for a quick break. I especially enjoy the quick mode and find that to be the most challenging game mode. The game is well polished, free and doesn\'t require any special permissions--what else do you need?
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Awesome game!
reviews.comment: A really fun and awesome game! Quick mode can get difficult pretty quickly but that\'s what makes it fun. I love the music in the game as well!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: Awesome app.  Reminds me of Pokemon Puzzle League in N64.  Simple, fast paced and addictive.  A++ would download again!  Actually, I\'d even buy this game for $.99 or some similar price range because it\'s that good!
reviews.author: A Google User
